::Kaiser::
       "Ah yes the great moment of decision.  I have chosen my form as well, 
a great beast from the mythos of future Earth."  He steps into the CR chamber 
to receive his new form.  Time passes and he steps out of the chamber.  He 
stands tall with the front half of his body that of an eagle and the back 
half that of a lion.  His entire body is a dull, nonreflective black.  His 
wings spread wide the new griffin steps forth onto the deck of the ship, his 
claws and talons clattering on the metal floor.  "Now I am ready."

--part1_105.22e35260.2b37daba_boundary
